      "role": "user",
      "content": "i’ve been looking at these spreadsheets for months and i’m starting to see patterns in the transaction logs that the supervisors never mention. it feels like these aren't just routine adjustments... its like we are actually positioning something for a massive shift in how the markets work. do you think they're keeping the bigger picture away from the people actually doing the data work?",
